snippet.title: Mason: Building Bricks Trailer
snippet.description:
Play on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1441400
Mason is a virtual brick set. You can play Mason the same way you play with LEGO bricks. With extensive collections of bricks and figures, you can build anything from a small structure to large cities.
